to Savinio</a>, <a href="/wiki/Philippe_Soupault" title="Philippe Soupault">Philippe Soupault</a>, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Takahashi_Shinkichi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Takahashi Shinkichi (page does not exist)">Takahashi Shinkichi</a>, <a href="/wiki/Giuseppe_Ungaretti" title="Giuseppe Ungaretti">Giuseppe Ungaretti</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ilarie_Voronca" title="Ilarie Voronca">Ilarie Voronca</a></dd>
