alas, Laura Wisner-Broyles, <i>Poetry Criticism</i>, Vol. 27, Gale Group Inc., 2000, <a href="http://www.enotes.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.enotes.com/" rel="nofollow">eNotes.com</a>; retrieved April 23, 2008</li>
