<li><a href="http://12.172.4.131/collection/browse_results.php?criteria=O%3AAD%3AE%3A13398&amp;page_number=1&amp;template_id=10&amp;sort_order=1" class="external text" title="http://12.172.4.131/collection/browse_results.php?criteria=O%3AAD%3AE%3A13398&amp;page_number=1&amp;template_id=10&amp;sort_order=1" rel="nofollow">Tristan Tzara drawings</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Museum_of_Modern_Art" title="Museum of Modern Art">Museum of Modern Art</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ubu.com/sound/tzara.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ubu.com/sound/tzara.html" rel="nofollow">Recordings of Tzara</a>, <a href="http://www.ubuweb.com/historical/dada/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ubuweb.com/historical/dada/index.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Dada Magazine</i></a>, <a href="http://www.ubu.com/ethno/discourses/tzara.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ubu.com/ethno/discourses/tzara.html" rel="nofollow"><i>A Note On Negro Poetry</i></a> and <a href="http://www.ubu.com/ethno/poems/01.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ubu.com/ethno/poems/01.html" rel="nofollow">Tzara's renditions of African poetry</a>, at <a href="/wiki/UbuWeb" title="UbuWeb">UbuWeb</a></li>
</ul>


